channel.title: elite784's web logs!
channel.description: another really simple syndication feed of web logs from somebody on the internet. copy the link to this page to your prefered rss syndicator to subscribe!
channel.p: a Really Simple Syndication feed, or RSS feed, is a kind of feed you can subscribe to get updates from using an RSS agregating program or app. this allows webmasters to let you know of new things on their site without you having to get on here regularly to look for the updates yourself! for example, this feed i use to let you know of new blogs i write!

item.title: i went to a movie about miku and 24 or so other characters in a len cosplay i made with things mostly laying around the house
item.description: 5 months of monitoring (funny). five months of waiting. finally... i can say "i watched the project sekai movie!" this blog isnt a review of the movie, more so it documents what the hell happened these past 5 months ive been waiting for it, and the cosplay i made with mostly scraps and reggo clothes in my closet
